<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 12:34:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着伊朗战争担忧的缓解，比特币跃升至 71,000 美元以上</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-10/bitcoin-jumps-back-above-70-000-as-iran-war-worries-ease</link><description>由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普发表评论后对伊朗战争的担忧有所缓解，比特币四天内首次升至 71,000 美元以上。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyUCeNpGi8Nw/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 03:34:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-10/bitcoin-jumps-back-above-70-000-as-iran-war-worries-ease</guid></item><item><title>伊朗战争有可能结束的迹象，比特币上涨</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/bitcoin-drops-to-7-day-low-as-oil-surges-on-iran-war-concerns</link><description>在唐纳德·特朗普总统暗示美国对伊朗的战争可能很快结束后，比特币与全球市场一起上涨。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iii.3pbxed8E/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2026 02:49:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/bitcoin-drops-to-7-day-low-as-oil-surges-on-iran-war-concerns</guid></item><item><title>人工智能的繁荣刺激了加密货币矿工的比特币销售威胁</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/ai-boom-spurs-bitcoin-sales-threat-at-miners-holding-8-billion</link><description>多年来，最大的比特币矿商在经营时都遵循着一种信念和商业模式：他们铸造的比特币值得持有，稀缺性会奖励耐心，数字货币的资产负债表积累本身就是一种竞争护城河。他们中的一些人建立了价值数亿美元的藏品。他们称之为财政战略。公牛队称之为信念。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyYdy0sIE6xI/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 20:44:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/ai-boom-spurs-bitcoin-sales-threat-at-miners-holding-8-billion</guid></item><item><title>石油交易在 24/7 加密货币交易所 Hyperliquid 上蓬勃发展</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/oil-trades-are-booming-on-24-7-crypto-exchange-hyperliquid</link><description>石油已成为 Hyperliquid 上的动量交易选择，该加密货币交易所迅速成为杠杆商品押注的全天候场所。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJytpyHR06f8/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2026 16:34:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/oil-trades-are-booming-on-24-7-crypto-exchange-hyperliquid</guid></item><item><title>Strategy 主要使用普通股购买 13 亿美元的比特币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/strategy-buys-1-3-billion-of-bitcoin-using-mostly-common-stock</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 加快了比特币购买步伐，斥资近 13 亿美元购买比特币，这是七周以来最大的一次购买，尽管早些时候承诺转向永久优先股，但再次依赖其普通股。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/izNJxT3BYZvY/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2026 14:30:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/strategy-buys-1-3-billion-of-bitcoin-using-mostly-common-stock</guid></item><item><title>稳定币支付公司 KAST 筹集 8000 万美元资金</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/stablecoin-payments-firm-kast-raises-80-million-in-funding</link><description>随着风险投资家继续向提供数字美元账户的初创公司注入资金，稳定币支付公司 KAST 在最新一轮融资中筹集了 8000 万美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/if2Fu7zdU0Fk/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2026 09:02:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/stablecoin-payments-firm-kast-raises-80-million-in-funding</guid></item><item><title>幻想体育公司 Underdog 收购衍生品交易所</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/fantasy-sports-firm-underdog-acquires-derivatives-exchange</link><description>幻想体育公司 Underdog 从运营 PredictIt 政治预测市场的 Aristotle Inc. 手中收购了一家受联邦政府监管的衍生品交易所和清算所。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i2tcYQI9H7Ig/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2026 13:00:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-09/fantasy-sports-firm-underdog-acquires-derivatives-exchange</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的世界自由金融项目让投资者陷入困境</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-08/trump-s-world-liberty-financial-project-puts-investors-in-a-bind</link><description>特朗普家族的旗舰加密项目再次面临质疑。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iybdDrNO3uIU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Mar 2026 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-08/trump-s-world-liberty-financial-project-puts-investors-in-a-bind</guid></item></channel></rss>